      "content": "idk i don't think it's just \"decay\"... it feels too specific. like, it's not just random stuff, it's stuff that actually matters. my old project files, some specific conversations... it's like they're targeting certain parts of my history. have you ever heard of companies doing something like \"digital scrubbing\" to basically erase people? like, making it so they don't exist in the digital record anymore?",
